{"commentv2": 1, "number": 6, "id": 276256, "nreplies": 9, "sticky": 0, "user": "42243", "body": "Medivh: Medivh is born into a wizard family. His father was named Nielas Aran (The shade of Aran) hes was a wizard in Azeroth. His mom was Aegwynn (750 years old omg...). He growned up in Azeroth and knows King Llane and Lord Lothar from the times when he were a child. \"Medivh\" means \"Guardian\" and Medivh is the \"Tirisfal Guardian\". His mom Aegwynn was a \"Guardian\" and as Lheonidas said (i couldn't have sayed it better myself)\r\nAegwynn, SHE was a confident mage\r\nHer mother killed the physical body of Sargeras, The Dark Titan\r\nHer mother broke the rule of guradian suceeding, \r\nHer mother chose the successor which was illegal\r\nHer mother chose her son to be the next guardian,\r\nAnd left him to live with other parents after she transfered the power of the guardians.\r\nMedivh was 14 he got that power so he couldn't take it and fainted for more than 20 years.\r\nMedivh's Staff: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=22589]Atish, Greatstaff of The Guardian[/url]", "date": "2008-04-23T12:03:29-05:00", "rating": 30, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Actually, Medivh means \"Keeper of Secrets\" :)", "creationdate": "2008-09-05T13:30:45-05:00", "id": 45675, "rating": 35, "commentid": 276256, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "166712", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Unless medivh had a gender change, im pretty sure Medivh's a boy.", "creationdate": "2009-08-04T11:04:26-05:00", "id": 113690, "rating": 24, "commentid": 276256, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "426611", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Those wizards do crazy things. How do you think Khadgar's Whisker's are all over the world?", "creationdate": "2009-11-04T15:56:58-06:00", "id": 130722, "rating": 21, "commentid": 276256, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "258919", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Correct Kajae. His pronouns and other words are all a bit...mixed up....in that paragraph of info. But we should all be able to understand what he meant.  But if you didn't, he mean't to say HIS mother (Aegwynn) did all those things and that Medivh WAS born into a wizard family.", "creationdate": "2010-11-14T16:26:20-06:00", "id": 192326, "rating": 4, "commentid": 276256, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Bombkirby", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "It's Atiesh, not Atish.", "creationdate": "2012-06-14T04:53:39-05:00", "id": 549728, "rating": 2, "commentid": 276256, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "George14", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2008-04-23T12:03:57-05:00", 1, "42243"]}
