{"commentv2": 1, "number": 13, "id": 547719, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "danroe", "body": "My favourite quote:\r\n\r\n[b]The time has come! Gul'dan! Order your warlocks to double their efforts! Moments from now, the gateway will open and your [i]Horde[/i] will be unleashed upon this ripe, unsuspecting world.[/b]", "date": "2009-01-05T06:39:29-06:00", "rating": 10, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Gul'dan and the Shadowmoon Council (said as [i]your warlocks[/i]) were the ones helping Medivh open a Warlock to a Portal from Draenor. The Skull of Gul'dan was later as a channeling totem used by Khadgar to destroy the Portals.", "creationdate": "2009-09-02T03:38:44-05:00", "id": 119825, "rating": 0, "commentid": 547719, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "111622", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Nitpicking here, but it's simply [b]Shadow[/b] Council, not Shadowmoon Council.", "creationdate": "2010-02-09T21:50:07-06:00", "id": 148234, "rating": 1, "commentid": 547719, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "DarthMuffin", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The Shadow Council is simply another name of the Shadowmoon Council; it just so happens that the Shadow Council is a slightly more well-known name.", "creationdate": "2011-10-05T10:40:45-05:00", "id": 268883, "rating": 0, "commentid": 547719, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Arikara", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 14, "id": 552216, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "SilentJ", "body": "Little-known fact: Cam Clarke did the voice acting for Medivh in the Black Morass, as well as the male blood elf voices. If his voice sounds familiar to anyone, you most likely have heard him in one of his many earlier roles. He starred as Leonardo in the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles cartoon, as well as Liquid Snake from Metal Gear Solid, and Simba from Kingdom Hearts II. Curiously, he also did some vocals for Everquest II.", "date": "2009-01-07T22:51:49-06:00", "rating": 22, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "He also voiced Kratos in Tales of Symphonia =)", "creationdate": "2009-02-07T23:12:13-06:00", "id": 78646, "rating": 6, "commentid": 552216, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Wezzy", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Also, [url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0164682/]Cam Clarke[/url] serves as the voice of Malygos in WoLK, and in TBC also provided the Blood Elf Male Player voice.  Another noteworthy voiceover outside of WoW would be his role as Prince Adam/He-man for the 2002 revival of the series.... Additional random trivia: this game also makes a reference to said character with the AB Battlemaster [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=20273]Adam Eternum[/url]... oh and his Horde counterpart [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=20274]Keldor the Lost[/url].", "creationdate": "2009-03-12T11:41:56-05:00", "id": 85121, "rating": 3, "commentid": 552216, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "LatroVir", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He (Kratos) also makes a cameo appearence in both Vesperia (Xbox 360) and Tales of Symphonia: Dawn of the New World (Wii).", "creationdate": "2009-07-08T14:42:15-05:00", "id": 108501, "rating": 0, "commentid": 552216, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "417373", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "LESSER BEINGS? INTRUDING HERE? A SHAME THAT YOU'RE EXCESS COURAGE DOES NOT COMPENSATE FOR YOU'RE STUPIDITY!", "creationdate": "2010-06-22T13:58:14-05:00", "id": 452684, "rating": 3, "commentid": 552216, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "crusader666", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "A nice pull quote, but Malygos is not Medivh.", "creationdate": "2011-08-02T16:03:15-05:00", "id": 256235, "rating": -1, "commentid": 552216, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "470840", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 15, "id": 735244, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "317120", "body": "For a dude with 6 million HP and a strong as hell shield, i don't see how he can just drop dead when his shield goes.", "date": "2009-06-02T15:03:41-05:00", "rating": 23, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Clothies are really, really, really squishy, and I bet maintaining a shield like that while channeling a portal to Outland, and while a demi-God has a death grip on your mind, is intense enough to make you die of shock if your shield breaks.", "creationdate": "2010-03-29T12:29:03-05:00", "id": 156355, "rating": 23, "commentid": 735244, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "476166", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Hopefully, he is or should be used to being mindcontrolled by Sargeras by the time he opens the Dark Portal. Also, i fail to picture Medivh as 'being shocked', much less dying of such a thing. Nah, just Blizzard being Blizzard 'bout this encounter.", "creationdate": "2011-10-05T10:44:45-05:00", "id": 268885, "rating": 0, "commentid": 735244, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Arikara", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "It would have been much better and more IC for Medivh/Sargeras if the \"defeat\" script went along the lines of: *shield fails and explodes outward in a deadly Arcane Explosion, killing players and dragons alike zone wide* \"ENOUGH! Years of work ruined because of meddling interlopers who do not understand of what I do here!\" *Medivh looks tired* \"Now I must go rest before I can begin again...\" *he teleports or flies away as a raven*.... If Blizzard ever redoes this dungeon, they should do something like that and give him a human model. XD", "creationdate": "2015-06-26T20:13:23-05:00", "id": 878820, "rating": 1, "commentid": 735244, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Coldaria", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
