{"commentv2": 1, "number": 18, "id": 1015504, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "Mystery21", "body": "medivh was a mage, right? then how come he's sorta a warlock too...?", "date": "2010-04-08T15:47:06-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Many powerful lore figures carry traits of multiple classes in the game (Arthas, Illidan, etc...), while it is true that Medivh shows some warlock abilities, it is proven that he is indeed a mage as he is carrying the mage version (you can see the red ribbon) of [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=22589#comments]Atiesh[/url] in the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/zone=2366]Black Morass[/url] encounter.", "creationdate": "2010-04-19T17:06:33-05:00", "id": 159759, "rating": 8, "commentid": 1015504, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Chromell", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Medivh was an incredibly powerful magic user. I'd he was more powerful than any mage/warlock currently in WoW, with the possible exception of Malygos and Kil'jaedan. He's way too powerful and knowledgeable about magic to really be any one single class.", "creationdate": "2010-06-12T19:01:17-05:00", "id": 167879, "rating": 6, "commentid": 1015504, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "614369", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Didn't we kick Malygos' ass though?  Also eww, my security code thing is \"bloody windbreak\". That's... horrifying.", "creationdate": "2010-07-19T16:10:21-05:00", "id": 455051, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1015504, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "128588", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Warlocks are basically a kind of corrupted mages. Both use Arcane magic, though the magic used by warlocks is corrupted, thus they get shadow stuff instead. Its not a big surprise with a creature like Sargeras inside him, then, that Medivh can do warlocky stuff.  Dunno what his deal with the raven form is, though.", "creationdate": "2011-10-05T10:48:31-05:00", "id": 268886, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1015504, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Arikara", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He is known to be familiar with both arcane magic (his parent's played a part here). Also familiar with the shamanistic magic (the warlock part, due to having an imaginary friend of his own - Sargeras hanging around for some time and a lovely bro-mance with Gul'Dan). Makes sense he is sorta warlock too.", "creationdate": "2015-02-26T01:39:16-06:00", "id": 847344, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1015504, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "NildaHostar", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 19, "id": 1069545, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "608793", "body": "I believe it's a carving of his raven from on the end of atiesh", "date": "2010-06-30T18:43:06-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Yes it is, it can be seen clearly in the cinematic of Medivh warning Terenas about the incoming Legion and Scourge and advising them to go to Kalimdor.", "creationdate": "2010-07-24T16:43:00-05:00", "id": 174750, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1069545, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Chromell", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 20, "id": 1233182, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Feralterror", "body": "Medivh is called and called himself too, that he is \"The Last Guardian\". He was wrong. He got a son, Med'an. Right now Med'an is the guardian. Medivh fell in love with the half draenai half orc Garona and so got the kid called Med'an. Medan is quarter draenai quarter orc half human. Probably he didn't knew himself that he had a son. As he called himself the last guardian he probably didn't knew that Garona was pregment.", "date": "2010-12-14T12:55:24-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 21, "id": 1529838, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "arkhi", "body": "Medivh here is voiced by Cam Clarke, the same voice actor for Nexus-Prince Shaffar and.... Blood elf males. How the BE male's voices ended up as a reference to gayness is beyond me.\r\n\r\nFor Kingdom Hearts fans, he voices Simba (Lion King) in KH:II.", "date": "2011-09-28T11:47:56-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 22, "id": 1921431, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "1192129", "body": "Hmmm... With the tweaking of Karazhan, and all of this time-travel background related to WoD, might Medivh be a boss, or the final boss of WoD?  That would be interesting", "date": "2013-11-26T14:33:11-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I think Blizzard may keep it for the next expansion - Burning Legion or so and make Medivh the first boss of it. There's still so much to explore and so many different ways to develop what is hapenning now in WoD. We shall see... \"soon (tm)\".", "creationdate": "2015-02-26T01:41:21-06:00", "id": 847346, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1921431, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "NildaHostar", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
