{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 326234, "nreplies": 13, "sticky": 0, "user": "FarseerLolotea", "body": "Oddly enough, this NPC (who's supposed to be a human) is built off of a modified night elf model rather than the human one.", "date": "2008-07-14T10:41:38-05:00", "rating": 30, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "looks rather fitting to me", "creationdate": "2008-07-29T11:33:53-05:00", "id": 41316, "rating": 5, "commentid": 326234, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "162030", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Also after you clean up the kara you can return to him and reset pices and play again.", "creationdate": "2008-08-28T05:23:26-05:00", "id": 44811, "rating": 4, "commentid": 326234, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Reunilana", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He was not a druid of the claw. He was the \"Last Guardian of Tirisfal\" a very powerful archmage who's job was to defend Azeroth from the Burning Legion.", "creationdate": "2008-10-28T08:09:46-05:00", "id": 53135, "rating": 14, "commentid": 326234, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ayline", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "And where did you get the idea that he was a druid of the claw? If he was a druid it would have been a druid of the Talon, IF any kind.  It is interesting to note, that out of Medivh's few actual visual appearances, he is voiced by the same person with the same pitch, during and after Sargeras taint(supposedly the echo of medivh is a reflection of him post-Sargeras). This is of course, Cam Clarke, the same voice actor for the Male Bloodelf characters.", "creationdate": "2008-10-29T2