{"commentv2": 1, "number": 29, "id": 2878499, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "SamashNZ", "body": "If anyone is still having issues soloing this encounter simply take control of a cleric, heal your footmen as needed. Heal your King when Medivh cheats and your pieces will eventually wipe out most of the enemy board. Jump on your second cleric, heal as much as you can and take control of the Conjuror (Queen) when the enemy Blackhand (King) gets two spaces from your King.", "date": "2019-03-24T01:10:52-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "There is a bug that makes pieces you have dismissed to despawn. I just use King and King only. Works 90% of the time.", "creationdate": "2019-11-25T17:48:38-06:00", "id": 1341067, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2878499, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Shardsy", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
