{"commentv2": 1, "number": 31, "id": 3163626, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "intothesunspots", "body": "If you're having trouble with the [spell=39331] debuff not falling off after you win, talk to the Shade of Medivh and ask him to reset the board. The debuff should disappear along with the remaining chess pieces.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[sub]Thanks to Lunne89 for posting this solution on the [spell=39331] page![/sub]", "date": "2019-10-12T18:02:17-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
